{
  "stem": "7739.1",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So everybody watching this made quite sure that they surrendered everything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Of course, when my turn came, I put in-- I had some money.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "My parents divided-- every child should have some money on them, and I threw in everything that I had.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "From there, they marched us to camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "There were some other incidents there that-- see, I was one of the smallest there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "They took me to my place of work-- my shift was from the first shift.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "This was late in the afternoon already.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "The shift was finished.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went from [NON-ENGLISH] the [NON-ENGLISH], to the [NON-ENGLISH] where they made raw steel.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they marched out the other Jewish people who were there from the first shift to walk towards camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Ukrainians picked me out, took me into the guard house, and they gave me a thorough search.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they think I might have some valuables on me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course, they didn't find anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What happened?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The group had left already.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They searched me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When I come out, there was nobody there, and I had to run to catch up with the column of people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there was a Jew on the loose, easy picking for anybody with a gun.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I still remember this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had to cross the railway tracks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a train coming, I had to wait until the train goes by and when I reached the column, I couldn't-- I couldn't run anymore.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they helped me out and we walked to the camp, which was situated on top of a cliff of a stone quarry and we had to-- we took a back road or something.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had to scale the quarry to go to camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
